      * IGNORE
     C           EUPID     CABNE*BLANK    @@JUMP
JWY   * IGNORE AUTOKINITON   (EPGID=* INDICATES THE ORDER PULLED FROM FORECAST)
 |   C           ENONY     IFEQ '5444'                     TOWER AUTO
 |   C           EPGID     ANDEQ*BLANK
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '5445'                     AUTO - KY
 |   C           EPGID     ANDEQ*BLANK
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '5446'                     AUTO - SHEPHARDSVILLE
 |   C           EPGID     ANDEQ*BLANK
JW   C**         ENONY     OREQ '5426'                     TSUSHO
 |   C**         EPGID     ANDEQ*BLANK
 |   C                     GOTO @@JUMP
JWY  C                     ENDIF
JWY   * STOP EDI
 |   C           ENONY     IFEQ '8005'                     WKW
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '6022'                     THAI SUMMIT
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '5253'                     LITENS (IN-21982)
