JWY  C                     ENDIF
JWY   * IGNORE ISUZU
 |   C           EPRTNR    IFEQ 'ISUZU'
 |   C           ENONY     ANDEQ'0531'
 |   C           EMANI     ANDEQ*BLANK
 |   C           EROS#     ANDNE'02'
