JWD   * TTAI
 |   C           ENONY     IFEQ '3511'                     TTTX
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '3512'                     TTCA
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '3550'                     TTMA
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '3556'                     TTAI
 JW  C           ENONY     OREQ '4022'                     YKATA(ATTAI)
JWT  C           ENONY     OREQ '5810'                     HITACHI
 |   C                     MOVELEODRN     DADEL#           PO#
 |   C                     MOVELEODRN     DAORDN           PO#
JWW  C                     MOVELESTAD     DAECS            CONTAINER
"    C                     MOVELESSPS     DAFLD3           DOCK
"    C                     MOVELEECS      DAFLD4           LOCATION
JWD  C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADD@@YY      DAKOYY
     C                     Z-ADD@@MM      DAKOMM
     C                     Z-ADD@@DD      DAKODD
     C                     Z-ADD@@HH      DAKOHH
     C                     Z-ADD@@MN      DAKOSS
