TCHLBC           ETOKU     IFEQ '3611'
TCHLBC                     MOVELECUNM     DACUNM
TCHLBC                     MOVELEPER4     DASUNM
TCHLBC                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELEN1MI     DACUNM
     C                     MOVELEN1SU     DASUNM
TCHLBC                     END
