TCHLBC           ETOKU     IFEQ '3611'
TCHLBC                     ELSE
TCHLAC                     MOVELEFLR2     DAREL#
TCHLBC                     END
      * 3556: TTAI
JWD  C           ENONY     IFEQ '3511'                     TTAI
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '3512'                     TTCA
 |   C           ENONY     OREQ '3550'                     TTMA
